<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Verify Your Thrive Account</title>
</head>
<body>
<p>Hi <b><%= it.username %></b></p>
<p>Thank you for choosing Thrive!</p>
<p>To ensure the security of your account and enable you to enjoy our services seamlessly, we need to verify your email
    address</p>
<p>Please click the link below to verify your email and complete the registration process:</p>
<a href="<%= it.confirmUrl %>" target="_blank">Verify Email</a>
<p>If the above link does not work, you can copy and paste the following URL into your browser:</p>
<p><%= it.confirmUrl %></p>
<p>If you did not request this verification or believe it to be a mistake, please disregard this email.</p>
<p>Thank you for choosing Thrive. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
</body>
</html>